'''Joe Hacker''' also credited as '''Joseph Hacker''' is a [[Wikipedia:Voice acting|Voice artist]] who appeared in numerous television shows, films, commercials, and radio plays. Hacker later became a dramatic arts professor at [[Wikipedia:University of Southern California|University of Southern California]].<ref name="USC School Bio" />

He was the voice of [[Han Solo/Legends|Han Solo]], [[Boba Fett/Legends|Boba Fett]], and [[Lo Khan]] in the [[Dark Empire: The Collector's Edition|Dark Empire audio adaptations]].<ref name="Dark Empire">[[Dark Empire (audio)|''Dark Empire '' audio drama]]</ref>

